What excites me about travel?

Whether I'm wandering aimlessly through the narrow streets of Stone Town, watching the fireworks of the Redantore Festival in Venice or admiring the breathtaking beauty of The Grand Mosque in Abu Dhabi. It is that feeling of self enrichment, enlightenment and excitement that only travel can bring! Sign me up
